  <note line="50" original="avattito (pī. ka.)" reference-line="56" id="9">
    <extra></extra>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="pī." source="pali text society">avattito</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">avattito</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>no_match</type>
    <snippet> katamā sakkāyadiṭṭhi? Assutavā bālo puthujjano yāva ariyadhamme akovido, so rūpaṃ attato samanupassati yāva viññāṇasmiṃ attānaṃ, so imesu pañcasu khandhesu attaggāho vā attaniyaggāho vā esohamasmi ekasmiṃ vasavattiko </snippet>
